metadata.name: #001 - The Original
metadata.description:
Idea of this Collection comes from this Animation I made a while ago. That's why its name is "The Original".

Emo Eyes are Hand Generated Animations.
Each piece has a Unique Design and Animation.

For any creature, eyes are the main assets showing deep Emotions, Charisma and sometimes by just looking into the Eyes you can feel the whole Story they want to tell.

Emo Eyes are small pieces of Animations each trying to tell that Story.
